Package: OlivierBorot
Title: Time Series Forecasting Using Weighted Nearest Neighbors (WNN)
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Olivier", "Borot", , "olivier.dominique.borot@email.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implementation of the Weighted Nearest Neighbors (WNN) algorithm 
    for time series forecasting as described in Talavera-Llames et al. (2016). 
    The package provides a simple class interface to create WNN models, fit them 
    to time series data, and generate forecasts.
